org.apache.paimon.flink.sink.cdc

Interface EventParser<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - CDC change event type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RichCdcMultiplexRecordEventParser, RichEventParser

    @Experimental
public interface EventParser<T>
    Parse a CDC change event to a list of DataFields or CdcRecord.
